Class LockedStackDepth

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.jpf.ListenerAdapter
      • gov.nasa.jpf.listener.LockedStackDepth
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JPFListener, PublisherExtension, SearchListener, VMListener

    public class LockedStackDepth
extends ListenerAdapter
    A listener that tracks information about the stack depth of when a lock is first acquired. If Writing a test for this class is very difficult. Hence, a lot of asserts are added.
